body:
Hi



when I'm opening the honeybee example files, I get the message, that the above file couldn't be loaded.

I've googled for it, but couldn't find anything about this on the net.

What does this means?



-rpict
topic: Unrecognized Object: ImageFromPath RCDVisualise - Plugin not found

replies.body:
I would say that you are missing installing EmbryoViz, the link is in the file you are opening (right side).

-A.

Hi A

I experienced the same problem and i don't understand what you said "the link is in the file you are opening", Could you explain more?  How can i fix this problem? Sorry, i am new in Ladybug.Thanks.

Open the example file 005_glareAnalysis and in the right side of the file you can see where you can download the plugin.

-A.
